openmediavault (7.0.5-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Issue #1736: Add support to create yearly scheduled shared
    folder snapshots.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Fri, 29 Mar 2024 19:22:33 +0100

