openmediavault (5.6.19-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Add 'WWN' column in disk and SMART devices pages. The column
    is hidden by default.
  * Improve SMART assessment. Take attribute 187 into account.
  * Issue #1125: Custom /etc/issue is being overwritten.
    Re-introduce environment variable OMV_ISSUE_APPLY_PRELOGIN_MESSAGE
    to prevent overwriting custom /etc/issue files.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Tue, 02 Nov 2021 13:58:59 +0100

