  * Issue #1079: Clear out the local repository of retrieved package
    files to fix the "... InRelease' changed its 'Suite' value from
    'stable' to 'oldstable'" message.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Tue, 27 Jul 2021 18:17:05 +0200

openmediavault (5.6.13-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Issue #986: Divert files modified by openmediavault to prevent
    problems when package updates want to override them.
  * Issue #1058: Disable SMTPUTF8 support in Postfix. This extension
    seems not supported by all email providers. Use the environment
    variable OMV_POSTFIX_MAIN_SMTPUTF8_ENABLED to customize this
    behavior.
  * Issue 1068: Display UID/GID in user/group data tables. The columns
    are hidden by default.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Sun, 04 Jul 2021 18:55:14 +0200

