  * Install security updates automatically. This can be disabled via
    the OMV_CRONAPT_SECURITY_UPGRADES_ENABLED environment variable.
  * Send an email to the administrator if the system needs to be
    rebooted to complete a package upgrade.
  * Rebuild SSH authorized keys even if the last public key of a user
    has been deleted.
  * Replace omv-update by omv-upgrade.

