 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Tue, 04 Aug 2020 20:46:45 +0200

openmediavault (5.5.5-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Various improvements.
  * Fix bug in 'omv.setup.fstab' when UUID is quoted.
  * Added the ability to have multiple WebGUI administrators.
    To do so simply assign users to the 'openmediavault-admin'
    group.
  * Introduce an UDEV rules database which fixes the problem of
    some USB PATA/SATA bridge controllers that they do not pass
    on the serial number of the attached disks.
  * Issue #769: Get overall health status of SAS drives.

