 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Wed, 15 Apr 2020 17:23:35 +0200

openmediavault (5.3.10-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix bug in the Python RPC error handling. This should fix the "got an
    unexpected keyword argument 'http_status_code'" issue.
  * Add user 'admin' to the Postfix recipient_canonical configuration.
  * Issue #670: Bonding interface configuration gets messed by VLAN.
  * Issue #671: Shared folders with blanks which are used as bind mounts
    are not formatted correct in /etc/fstab. Nevertheless it is not
    possible to mount such bind mounts because of an error in SaltStack,
    see #524, #566 or https://github.com/saltstack/salt/issues/54508.

