 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Wed, 13 Jun 2018 06:45:35 +0200

openmediavault (4.1.8.1-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix systemd monit.service issue.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Mon, 11 Jun 2018 08:49:09 +0200

openmediavault (4.1.8-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Issue #113: Reduce monit delay from 30 to 5 seconds after the daemon is
    (re-)started. This is a delay until monit starts monitoring the configured
    services. During this time to CLI tool was not useable and results in an
    socket not available error. To allow the monitored services to be started
    before monit is starting monitoring, it will be started at least by systemd.
    If there are still services that require more time to setup the delay
    can be customized via the environment variable OMV_MONIT_DELAY_SECONDS.
  * Reload the shared folder systemd mount units if the volume of the shared
    folder has been changed.
  * Issue #120: Grow mdadm RAID device adds new device as spare.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Sat, 26 May 2018 17:02:31 +0200

openmediavault (4.1.7-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Fix bug in Postfix when using port 465 (SSL/TLS).
  * Fix the pattern attribute in the JSON schemas according to the ECMA 262
    regular expression dialect.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Wed, 09 May 2018 09:31:03 +0200

openmediavault (4.1.6-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Various improvements.
  * Issue #95: Failed to read file '/tmp/bgstatus*' (size=0).

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Mon, 30 Apr 2018 18:18:51 +0200

openmediavault (4.1.5-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Update Material Design icons to version 2.2.43.
  * Issue #84: Perf. statistics/Disk usage tab: double label if the system
    disk has already a label
  * Issue #87: Use device file when resizing XFS/JFS filesystems.
  * Issue #88: Refactor RPC FileSystemMgmt::enumerateFilesystems() to speedup
    filesystem detection.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Tue, 10 Apr 2018 20:30:26 +0200

