 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Tue, 20 Mar 2018 20:02:18 +0100

openmediavault (4.1.1-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Various improvements.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Sat, 17 Mar 2018 09:17:54 +0100

openmediavault (4.1.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Update locales.
  * Replace ifquery command in 'omv-mkconf issue' script.
  * Create RRD graphs for filesystems with whitespaces in their labels.
  * Increase package version to 4.1.0 according to semantic versioning
    (https://semver.org/).
  * Refactor and cleanup many things in the PHP API.
  * Add SCSI generic backend (experimental to support such devices in the
    S.M.A.R.T. page in a later step)
  * Enhance API docs.
  * Rename many PHP interfaces related to the storage backend from IXxxYyyZzz
    to XxxYyyZzzInterface according to PSR (PHP Standards Recommendations),
    see https://www.php-fig.org/psr. All others will be renamed in OMV5
    because this would be too much work for existing OMV4 plugins right now.
  * Rename \OMV\Debugable to \OMV\DebugTrait.

 -- Volker Theile <volker.theile@openmediavault.org>  Sun, 11 Feb 2018 19:54:12 +0100

