openmediavault (3.0.60) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix render bug in Chrome 56 (EXTJS-23628). Thanks to BobR and kleins from
    the Sencha ExtJS forum to contribute a fix to the ExtJS community.
  * Various improvements.
  * Introduce configuration database migration backend.
  * Notify FTP TLS and BAN list configuration changes.
  * Use TLSv1.2 for secure FTP connections.
  * Add catalán language support.
  * Galician users must reselect the language in the WebUI.
  * Mantis 0001657: Append 'nofail' to NFS bind mounts to prevent systemd to
    start into the emergency-mode due to unmet dependencies.
  * Mantis 0001658: filesystem class vs mountpoint class.
  * Mantis 0001659: Adapt network backend to support predictable network
    interface names.
  * Mantis 0001666: Cannot creaet NFS shares of btrfs subvolumes with names
    prefixed by an '@' symbol.
  * Mantis 0001671: Use CSS to animate the guru meditation box. Thanks to
    digisam for the contribution.
  * Mantis 0001673: Delete PHP session files during bootup.

